name: future Sadness.
description: I am thinking about the future, what will happen in the future, I am very worried about the current situation.I am very worried about how this world will change in the future.I feel like this world has gone really crazy. feel life now is much different from how I felt before. and it makes me sad. there are positive things from the advancement of a technology, but on the other hand a lot has to be sacrificed for it.
